hill">Becky Hill</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/steve-lacy">Steve Lacy</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/central-cee">Central Cee</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/muna">MUNA</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-snuts">The Snuts</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/tion-wayne">Tion Wayne 等乐队也将在联合音乐节上演出。</a></p><p>与此同时， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/arlo-parks">Arlo Parks</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/easy-life">Easy Life</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/frank-turner">Frank Turner</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/holly-humberstone">Holly Humberstone</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/mimi-webb">Mimi Webb</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-amazons">The Amazons</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/caity-baser">Caity Baser</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sea-girls">Sea Girls</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/palaye-royale">Palaye Royale</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/bakar">Bakar</a>等也都将参加演出。</p><p>您可以<a href="https://ticketmaster-uk.tm7559.net/c/2862475/431519/7559?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.co.uk%2Freading-and-leeds-festival" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在这里</a>找到剩余的节日门票。</p><p>这篇文章<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/heres-the-early-weather-forecast-for-reading-leeds-2023-3485288">“这是雷丁和利兹 2023 年的早期天气预报”</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
